s/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a0fcd19a25ce832ec6aa08e386799e53844072","tid":1881722,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6fe3a5f6dec1f40030c56ffc5b4c1bd21009017","tid":1881722,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e3a7e2e291cd5e47bf0544562b3b8153e49c66","tid":1881722,"uid":53214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692a089790745ac7aa4f37c9a9f94950c54a2bdf","tid":1881722,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a20c6cc627870f30b55267d24b247eb5a903bda","tid":1881722,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6436193e5123664ceaf111454391b5ed0b27716","tid":1881722,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"清談節目好似冇限要準確，新聞時事節目先有。"},{"pid":"8f3908421b2963649cd6b3423157db1cb8153480","tid":1881722,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"✉️和你投訴✉️ 6號話沙士來自香港😡‼️<br />\n<br />\nwebmaster@ofca.gov.hk<br />\nBroadcastcomplaint@ofca.gov.hk<br />\ntvbpr@tvb.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n主旨：投於TVB節目散播失實資訊<br />\n<br />\n在2020年2月15日TVB 節目《後生仔傾吓偈》播出的一集中，主持陸浩明談及 2003 年沙士時，謊稱沙士(SARS)的起源地為香港，其原句為「因為嗰時香港係病毒源頭。」<br />\n<br />\n當年SARS悲痛一役，導致數名醫護人員因公殉職，更有無數醫護人員事後留下後遺症。今天，另一波的疫症重臨香港，陸先生卻在此時發布失實言論，不但扭曲當年事實，傷害了在SARS其間殉職醫護家屬的心，更嚴重打擊現時在前線抗疫的醫護人員的士。<br />\n<br />\n由於該節目深受年青人喜愛，有關失實資訊將發放錯誤資訊於年青的觀眾群中，嚴重毒害下一代！其實此節目已經不是第一次發放失實的資訊，並且經常談及一止色情的中內容，十分嘔心，根本應該予以取締。<br />\n<br />\nTVB作為全港暫時仍是最大的電視廣播媒體，卻未能有效監管其下藝人的失言失德，在節目中發布失實資訊，本人要求通訊事務管理局予以重罰！<br />\n<br />\n你個名<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n特別鳴謝友台「我要投訴你！1823投訴攻略」channel<br />\n<br />\n我要投訴你！頻道： @comp1823<br />\n我要投訴你！公海： @comp1823gp<br />\n<br />\n查詢： @iluv1823"}]}